CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F403A1783676986
OL,3,CMan charged with murder after pet shop
OL,4,Cowner dies in road collision
OL,6,FNo plea was entered in court today and
OL,7,Fhe was remanded in custody once again
OL,8,Funtil his next appearance on Wednesday
OL,9,F(8 July) at Bristol Crown Court.
OL,11,FPet shop owner Barbara Mullaney has
OL,12,Fbeen named locally as the person
OL,13,Fkilled in the crash on the B4696 at
OL,14,Fjust after 6pm on June 30.
OL,16,FWiltshire Police said the collision
OL,17,Finvolved an orange Peugeot 107
OL,18,Ftravelling southbound and a black
OL,19,FVauxhall Astra travelling northbound.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/5
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,404,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40303
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F403A1783676986
OL,3,CMan charged with murder after pet shop
OL,4,Cowner dies in road collision
OL,6,FThe driver of the Peugeot, a woman in
OL,7,Fher 70s, was declared dead at the
OL,8,Fscene.
OL,10,FA passenger in the Vauxhall, a teenage
OL,11,Fgirl, suffered serious injuries in the
OL,12,Fcollision and was taken to hospital
OL,13,Fbefore being discharged.
OL,15,FDetective Chief Inspector Phil Walker
OL,16,Fsaid: "This is a significant
OL,17,Fdevelopment in our investigation, and
OL,18,FI would like to thank the support of
OL,19,Fthe local community who have provided
OL,20,Finformation to us.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/5
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,404,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40304
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F403A1783676986
OL,3,CMan charged with murder after pet shop
OL,4,Cowner dies in road collision
OL,6,F"I would like to apologise for the
OL,7,Fconfusion regarding the direction of
OL,8,Ftravel of the vehicles on the B4696 in
OL,9,Four earlier appeals. This detail has
OL,10,Fbeen corrected but, for clarity, the
OL,11,FPeugeot 107 was travelling south-bound
OL,12,Ftowards Royal Wootton Bassett, and the
OL,13,FVauxhall Astra was travelling
OL,14,Fnorthbound towards Cricklade.
OL,16,F"I'd like to repeat my appeal for
OL,17,Fwitnesses with dash-cam in the Lydiard
OL,18,FPlain area of the B4696 and in the
OL,19,Fareas of Cricklade High Street and
OL,20,FPurton High Street on June 30.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/5
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,404,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40305
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F403A1783676986
OL,3,CMan charged with murder after pet shop
OL,4,Cowner dies in road collision
OL,6,F"Finally, I would like to again extend
OL,7,Fmy condolences to the family and
OL,8,Ffriends of the victim and thank them
OL,9,Ffor their patience and dignity during
OL,10,Fthis early stage of the investigation."
OL,12,FThe Wiltshire force has made a
OL,13,Fmandatory referral to the Independent
OL,14,FOffice for Police Conduct (IOPC) due
OL,15,Fto previous involvement with the
OL,16,Fsuspect.
